  "source_notes": "James Elliot quotes him, taken from his hospital records (3/1994), with time 12:45 pm. Same source is quoted in CAC.\\nIn March 2022 the Canadian astrologer Solange Lussier wrote \"J'ai personnellement eu entre les mains l'acte de naissance de cette personne en 2008 ou 09.  .. L'acte était en possession de Jacqueline Royer, qui a rencontré monsieur Charest durant des vacances en Espagne... À noter que le 0h45 est l'heure imprimée sur le certificat\" (I had the BC in my hands in 2008 or 2009. The BC had been sent to J.R. who had met M. Charest during a holiday in Spain. Please note that 0h45 was the time shown on the BC.)\\nWe hold this, despite the lack of physical evidence, as more probable. Solange Lussier insists that there was a zero in the time, as 0:45.\\n",
